AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: GrossProfitMarginPercentage
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @RET260388
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[GrossProfitMarginPercentage] AS IIF( ISEMPTY([Measures].[CustomerInvoiceLineAmountAccountingCurrency]), NULL, (([Measures].[CustomerInvoiceLineAmountAccountingCurrency] - [Measures].[CostOfGoodsSoldAccountingCurrency] - [Measures].[SalesTaxIncludedInCustomerInvoiceLineAmountAccountingCurrency]) / [Measures].[CustomerInvoiceLineAmountAccountingCurrency]) ), VISIBLE = 1 ;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: AverageDaysLateConfirmedShipDate
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: Average difference from the confirmed ship date to the packing slip receipt date
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343819
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[AverageDaysLateConfirmedShipDate] AS IIF( ISEMPTY([Measures].[CustomerPackingSlipLinesCount]) OR [Measures].[CustomerPackingSlipLinesCount] = 0, NULL, ([Measures].[DaysLateConfirmedShipDate] / [Measures].[CustomerPackingSlipLinesCount]) ), VISIBLE = 1;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: AverageDaysLateRequestedShipDate
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: Average difference from the requested ship date to the packing slip receipt date
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343741
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[AverageDaysLateRequestedShipDate] AS IIF( ISEMPTY([Measures].[CustomerPackingSlipLinesCount]) OR [Measures].[CustomerPackingSlipLinesCount] = 0, NULL, ([Measures].[DaysLateRequestedShipDate] / [Measures].[CustomerPackingSlipLinesCount]) ), VISIBLE = 1;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: AllSalesOrderLines
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: Number of sales order lines with at least one related packing slip and not of status Open order
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @GLS180091
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[AllSalesOrderLines] AS SUM ( {[SalesOrderLines].[Status].&[2], [SalesOrderLines].[Status].&[3]}, ([Measures].[SalesOrderLinesCount], [SalesOrderLines].[ShippedInFull].[All], [SalesOrderLines].[PrecisionOfShippingBasedOnRequestedDateOf1stPackingSlip].[All], [SalesOrderLines].[PrecisionOfShippingBasedOnConfirmedDateOf1stPackingSlip].[All]) ), VISIBLE = 1 ;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: SalesOrderLinesShippedInFull
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: Percent shipped in full of sales order lines with at least one related packing slip and not of status Open order
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @GLS180092
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[SalesOrderLinesShippedInFull] AS IIF( ISEMPTY([Measures].[AllSalesOrderLines]) OR [Measures].[AllSalesOrderLines] = 0, NULL, (100 * SUM ( {[SalesOrderLines].[Status].&[2], [SalesOrderLines].[Status].&[3]}, ([Measures].[SalesOrderLinesCount], [SalesOrderLines].[ShippedInFull].&[1]) ) / [Measures].[AllSalesOrderLines]) ), VISIBLE = 1;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: SalesOrderLinesNotShippedInFull
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: Percent not shipped in full of sales order lines with at least one related packing slip and not of status Open order
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @GLS180093
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[SalesOrderLinesNotShippedInFull] AS IIF( ISEMPTY([Measures].[AllSalesOrderLines]) OR [Measures].[AllSalesOrderLines] = 0, NULL, (100 * SUM ( {[SalesOrderLines].[Status].&[2], [SalesOrderLines].[Status].&[3]}, ([Measures].[SalesOrderLinesCount], [SalesOrderLines].[ShippedInFull].&[0]) ) / [Measures].[AllSalesOrderLines]) ), VISIBLE = 1;
